{"article_id":"2fA49Nc8KtHo5usN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford ' s lawyer said Thursday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"she does want to testify to the Senate next week about her allegations against Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett M. Kavanaugh ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"as long as she is given assurances about her safety and the fairness of the proceedings .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"But she said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Monday won ' t work for Ms. Blasey Ford due to security concerns ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"rejecting the day","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Judiciary Committee Chairman Charles E. Grassley has set for the showdown .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Instead , she is eyeing Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"\" She wishes to testify ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"provided that we can agree on terms","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that are fair","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and which ensure her safety , \"","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Debra Katz , Ms. Blasey Ford ' s attorney wrote in an email to the committee .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Republicans continued to prepare for a hearing ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"with two sources saying","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"lawmakers were eyeing asking a nonpartisan outside lawyer","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to conduct the questioning of Ms. Blasey Ford and Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"That could avoid the spectacle","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"of male senators","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"being forced into a testy back-and-forth with the woman","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"who says","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"she was sexually assaulted by Judge Kavanaugh","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"when they were both high school students .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"But one senior Senate aide told The ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford prefers to be quizzed by the lawmakers .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"She also doesn ' t want to testify in the same room as Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"insists","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that witnesses","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"she says","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"were present at the time of the attack","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"be subpoenaed","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and also wishes to have no time limit","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"placed on her opening statement .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"\" The committee doesn ' t issue subpoenas in the process","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"of considering nominations","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"- that is a nonstarter .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Other alleged witnesses have made clear","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"they have no intention","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"of testifying , \"","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"the senior staffer told The Times .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"\" It only makes sense for the accused to respond to the charges","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"so Judge Kavanaugh would surely follow Dr. Ford . \"","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"It ' s not clear whether GOP senators are receptive to her lawyers ' requests for a different date .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"\" We are happy","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that Dr. Ford ' s attorneys are now engaging with the committee , \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Taylor Foy , a spokesman for the committee , told The Associated Press .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"The committee ' s GOP staff had been trying to reach Ms. Blasey Ford and her lawyers in the days","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"since she went public with her accusation .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"They say","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"they have offered her the chance","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to have a public or closed-door hearing ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and have asked to have investigators interview her","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"- including in California ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"if that ' s her wish .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"They also canceled a committee vote on Judge Kavanaugh ' s nomination ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"which had been scheduled for Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"in order to give Ms. Blasey Ford an opportunity","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to be heard .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"After asking for a hearing ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford , through her lawyers , announced a number of preconditions ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"including demanding multiple witnesses","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"and insisting the FBI investigate her claims","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"before she would agree to testify .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Republicans rejected those","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"they were sticking with their plans for Monday .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford ' s lawyers then changed tactics Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"sending the letter to the committee","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"she is not averse to testifying next week ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"but must have her safety and the fairness of the proceedings assured .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"The letter was first reported by The New York Times .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford ' s attorneys said","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"she has faced threats","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"and has had to hire security and leave her home .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Key Senate Democrats sent a letter to the FBI on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"asking them to investigate those threats as acts of intimidation of a key witness .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"They also said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that could give the FBI a backdoor opportunity","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"to investigate Ms. Blasey Ford ' s original assault allegation .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"\" The bureau should promptly investigate these potential crimes against Dr. Blasey Ford","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and provide updates to Congress","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"as appropriate , \"","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"the Democrats said .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford has declined so far to talk to committee investigators about her account ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"but staffers have spoken to Judge Kavanaugh and several other people","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford has suggested","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"were witnesses .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Two of those individuals have given statements to the committee","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"denying having been witnesses to the behavior","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford alleged .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh has also vehemently denied the accusation ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"and so far no corroborating witness has publicly come forward","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"to back up Ms. Blasey Ford ' s account .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"In a letter Thursday to Mr. Grassley , Judge Kavanaugh said","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"he will be at Monday ' s hearing","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"and is eager to defend his integrity .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"\" I continue to want a hearing as soon as possible ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"so that I can clear my name , \"","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"the nominee said .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford first made her allegations in communications to Democrats on Capitol Hill in July ,","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"but the information was not used until just before the first scheduled vote on Judge Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"- and well after he sat for a week of hearings .","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"Rep. Anna Eshoo , a California Democrat","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"who was one of those","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"who got the information in July ,","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"said Thursday","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"she promised to keep the woman ' s identity private .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"Ms. Eshoo said","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"she thinks","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford ' s testimony should take place in public","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"for the American people to view .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"\" I believe","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"that my constituent Dr. Ford will testify .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"any senator wants to bear the burden","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"of being accused of not being fair , \"","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Ms. Eshoo told KCBS radio Thursday .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":235,"left":217,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":130,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":120,"right":129,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":119,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":124,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":3,"right":122,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":4,"right":121,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":8,"right":126,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":9,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":174,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":158,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":139,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":13,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nu